k can impose a constraint, and a descriptive value can monitor model behavior. The profile does not collapse these roles into one score. We test the core outputs by injecting known failures at increasing strengths. A useful output should react to its target failure and remain unchanged under predeclared invariance controls. Seven output axes meet these criteria in nine nonredundant tests on 80 held-out song groups. Complementary development stress tests yield two broader lessons. First, timing must be anchored", "stderr": "\nShell cwd was reset to /inspire/qb-ilm/project/video-generation/chenxie-25019/hyr/iHateTheWorld555.github.io", "interrupted": false, "isImage": false, "noOutputExpected": false}}
